The,New,York,State,Office,of,the,CIO,announced,a,technology,initiative,themed,Empire,which,targets,social,networking,participation,and,collaboration,as,part,of,an,overall,theme,of,transparency,and,open,government,The,Empire,site,is,a,platform,for,users,to,submit,discuss,and,refine,ideas,regarding,policy,specific,technology,or,project,suggestions,state,wide,or,agency,specific,feedback,The,Empire,Tech,Talk,API,provides,methods,for,obtaining,data,from,the,site,for,use,in,mashups,and,other,consumable,formats,The,API,uses,JavaScript,protocol,and,responses,are,formatted,in,JSON